♻️ Give for Good
Give for Good is a community-driven platform where users can share their unused, unwanted, or surplus goods for free. The goal is to reduce waste and promote a culture of sharing and sustainability.

🌟 Features
🧺 Share Unused Items
Users can list items they no longer need, allowing others in the community to claim them for free. It's simple, ethical, and eco-friendly.

💬 Real-time Chat
Built-in chat system lets users communicate directly, making it easy to coordinate pickups and ask questions.

🏆 Gamification
Encouraging active participation:

Earn points for listing items, completing giveaways, and engaging with the community.

Points are showcased on a leaderboard, promoting healthy competition and community contribution.

📱 Clean, Modern UI
User-friendly interface that works smoothly across devices.

